1. Preprocessing & Normalization (Numerically)
Input:
python
Copy
Edit
import numpy as np

X = np.array([[1, 200], [2, 300], [3, 400], [4, 500]], dtype=float)
y = np.array([10, 20, 30, 40], dtype=float)
Normalization (Min-Max Scaling):
